 10 g cloves, 25 cardamom seeds (shelled), 1 star anise, and 20 black peppercorns then grind <strong>1 min 30 sec\/speed 10<\/strong>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula. If necessary, grind again <strong>30 sec<\/strong><strong>\/speed 10<\/strong>. Store in a sealed container.<br>"],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","1h 25m","10 slices"]}